{"tid":968202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"狂轟37球！阿古路Big 6殺手","createTime":"2019-01-04T05:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-04T17:40:14.000Z","uid":5649,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"53e3333de9ca6136a68f1b096b89ca447c149fad","tid":968202,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:03:42.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=XGiFqoyZeDLaOdCvfDe1KUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=eeb534bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】曼城如果想長期處於爭標位置，怎可缺少阿古路？連帶今次攻破利物浦大門，阿古路歷來鬥Big 6的入球數目增至37球，無人能出其右。<br />\n<br />\n阿古路（Sergio Aguero）在曼城大戰利物浦的比賽先開紀錄，打從2011/12年球季計起，阿古路在聯賽對其他Big 6球隊共入37球，比其他球員在Big 6大戰至少多入16球，緊隨其後的是哈利卡尼。須知道Big 6之間對撼不乏「6分波」，由此可見此君在曼城爭冠的重要程度。<br />\n<br />\n這名30歲阿根廷射手向是利物浦剋星，過去7次代表曼城主場鬥紅軍都有斬獲，而今仗的入球令他職業生涯聯賽入球達250球，當中153球來自英超。<br />\n<br />\n為曼城奠勝的利萊辛尼同樣出色，這名22歲德國鋒將自上季起為曼城上陣的25場主場聯賽中，合共參與26個入球（9入球17助攻），數字相當驚人。<br />\n<br />\nVS BIG 6入球榜<br />\n1）阿古路　　37球<br />\n2）哈利卡尼　21球<br />\n3）朗尼　　　20球<br />\n4）尹佩斯　　18球<br />\n5）夏薩特　　17球"},{"pid":"f1fe1db94588a97464321ad9acea769db8ed9ff9","tid":968202,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:06:35.000Z","msg":"肥絲召喚"},{"pid":"9855dba6a3e902b8f213a30c5da9c1342039948b","tid":968202,"uid":38143,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"Pussy係咪唯一一個對big6都有波入"},{"pid":"84ae078166dcbbd42887194778e29093b742bfa9","tid":968202,"uid":33749,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9855dba6a3e902b8f213a30c5da9c1342039948b","tid":968202,"uid":38143,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:06:41.000Z","msg":"Pussy係咪唯一一個對big6都有波入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T05:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"